===========================================================
OVERVIEW
-----------------------------------------------------------
CBB Model v4 is a fully automated NCAA basketball betting
model that:

1. Scrapes efficiency ratings from BartTorvik
2. Scrapes daily NCAA schedules from BartTorvik
3. Pulls consensus betting markets from The Odds API
4. Cleans and structures advanced efficiency metrics
5. Normalizes team names across all data sources
6. Maintains deterministic team identity registry
7. Projects game-level spreads and totals
8. Applies structural margin weighting
9. Applies advanced matchup factor adjustments
10. Applies home court advantage
11. Applies recency adjustment using WAB differential
12. Applies dynamic spread bias centering
13. Anchors totals to market mean dynamically
14. Calculates win probability using logistic model
15. Computes market edge vs model projections
16. Generates spread and total betting signals
17. Builds full engine diagnostic slate
18. Automatically syncs outputs to Google Sheets
19. Runs automated integrity checks each pipeline run
20. Maintains append-only results tracking
21. Provides interactive Streamlit dashboard
22. Supports admin-controlled daily lock selections
23. Includes historical data infrastructure for expansion

The system is modular, deterministic, and production-stable.

