edge_engine.py
-----------------------------------------------------------
Calculates betting edges and produces engine slate.

INPUT:

    data/projections.csv
    data/market_odds.json
    data/efficiency_table.csv

TEAM MATCHING:

Uses team_normalizer.team_key()

FUNCTIONS:

- Merge projections with market odds
- Round spreads and totals to half points
- Compute spread and total edges
- Compute OE and DE efficiency diagnostics

Edge formulas:

spread_edge =
    model_spread - market_spread

total_edge =
    model_total - market_total


OUTPUT FILES:

data/engine.csv
Full model slate with diagnostics.

Columns:

    Game Time
    Home
    Away
    Spread
    Total
    OE Diff
    DE Diff
    Spread Edge
    Model Spread
    Total Edge
    Model Total


data/qualified_bets.csv
Filtered bets meeting edge thresholds.


